                "invention-title": [
                    "Method and system for purifying mixed gas containing H2 and CO2 and application of system",
                    "含H2和CO2的混合气的纯化方法和系统及其应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of gas separation, in particular to a method and system for purifying mixed gas containing H2 and CO2, and the method comprises the following steps: (1) feeding the mixed gas containing H2 and CO2 into a pressure swing adsorption unit to trap heavy components containing CO2; and (2) feeding the H2-containing light component gas into an electrochemical purification unit. According to the purification method, high-purity hydrogen and high-purity carbon dioxide product gas can be obtained while high-yield hydrogen is obtained; the two units are coupled and cooperated to prepare high-purity hydrogen and capture CO2 at the same time, and the purification method not only realizes separation of different components such as H2 and CO2, but also can realize pressurization of hydrogen to be supplied to a fuel cell for use."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及气体分离技术领域，具体涉及一种含H2和CO2的混合气的纯化方法和系统，该方法包括：(1)将含H2和CO2的混合气送入变压吸附单元捕集包括CO2的重组分；(2)然后将含H2的轻组分气体送入电化学纯化单元。通过该纯化方法可以在获得高收率氢气的同时得到高纯氢气和高纯二氧化碳产品气；两个单元耦合协同在制备高纯氢气的同时实现CO2捕集，该纯化方法不仅实现H2、CO2等不同组分的分离，同时可实现氢气增压供给燃料电池使用。"
                }
            ]
